Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.49,0:01:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,訓話?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.87,0:01:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是戰事都起於邊境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.33,0:01:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邊境…
