Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.09,0:11:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不工作，還能睡整天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.77,0:12:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還不是閒著揮木刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.65,0:12:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經把今天的工作\N全部做完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.94,0:12:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.45,0:12:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我平時就鍛鍊身心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.87,0:12:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓自己保持在隨時可接受\N微風號出擊命令的狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.42,0:12:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.05,0:12:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.51,0:12:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茶太溫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.06,0:12:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們每天過這種安逸生活\N對嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.98,0:12:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克魯斯部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.57,0:12:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校級的情報員名單列出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.24,0:12:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀幕請使用326頻道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.20,0:12:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不敢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.40,0:13:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.53,0:13:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫我連絡情報資料管理課的\N由理子.絲達少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.45,0:13:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久沒來這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.79,0:13:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三船中將，新型巡洋艦的配備\N我們而言是攸關生死問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.09,0:13:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說軍方打算在\N下次幕僚會議做最終決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.01,0:14:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不必急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.72,0:14:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正軍方一定要重新編組\N而且好壞都無從選擇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.56,0:14:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍方將新型高速巡洋艦建造計畫\N稱為R號計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.03,0:14:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,談到最後\N一定會變成重新編組配備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這之間的討論\N是會花上一段時間的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.74,0:14:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼… 我們在幕僚會議上\N就得更加小心才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.74,0:14:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.54,0:14:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是成功的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.37,0:14:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是我們司令部主導權大大增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.21,0:14:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三船中將你發言的份量\N會更加重大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.88,0:14:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚真想跟您你慢慢吃火鍋慶祝呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.64,0:14:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.77,0:14:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼，海軍基地燒起來了!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.04,0:15:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旺克宰相，時間到\N請到大廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.80,0:16:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家安靜，皇帝陛下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.85,0:16:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旺克，剛才你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.48,0:16:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在應該是試探和平協定的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.74,0:16:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道我們的帝國戰士\N是怎樣的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.08,0:16:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，皇帝陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特姆大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.84,0:16:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想情況你應該聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是前天運輸船被破壞之前與之後\N所竊聽到的檢樣資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.31,0:16:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請把這個無法鑑別的訊號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.10,0:16:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟這邊的帶磁流星群的\N原始拷貝做徹底比較分析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.94,0:16:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是意外嗎，課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.61,0:17:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我要你去調查的呀\N蓋茲中士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,調查部說那是事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.37,0:17:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克魯斯部長希望知道分析部門的看法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.87,0:17:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是部長的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.42,0:17:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他特地調來情報資料管理的負責官員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可說是非常認真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他找誰來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.45,0:17:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,座標點1310到258
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由巡航速度切換為亞空間移動\N倒數5秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.87,0:17:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三、二、一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.80,0:18:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法離開亞空間，消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.13,0:18:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香取中尉\N程序錯誤，請再做一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.51,0:18:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解，我再從頭開始設定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.39,0:18:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,座標點1310當258
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.31,0:18:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由巡航速度切換為亞空間移動，倒數5秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.73,0:18:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.52,0:18:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會被你拿走34分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.40,0:18:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡構造不同嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.86,0:18:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輸給你，我很懊惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.16,0:18:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂，你看這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.29,0:18:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要看清楚哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.75,0:18:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.46,0:18:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.34,0:18:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎，作弊用的小抄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.64,0:18:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你只拿了34分嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.64,0:18:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這真是傑作呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.61,0:19:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼好笑的，總比19分好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.94,0:19:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要提19分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在問題不是分數多寡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想打嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.78,0:19:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要打嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.62,0:19:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，香取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.21,0:19:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經聽說96式的事了\N聽說你們要重考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.96,0:19:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們沒問題，隨時可以重考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自欺欺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.35,0:19:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼了，怎麼一臉沉重的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.39,0:19:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次要更新亞空間航法系統\N我正在接受訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.27,0:19:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但… 還是跟不上呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.23,0:19:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,微風號要裝上那個系統嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.86,0:19:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想不能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.61,0:19:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞空間航行速度加倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.65,0:19:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以微風號的船身\N一定受不了那速度的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.78,0:19:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你學了也沒用嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.74,0:19:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍方到底在想什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.54,0:20:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法，不學無法上太空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.75,0:20:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀，沒有香取在\N微風號是動不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.34,0:20:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.13,0:20:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，你們的重考也要好好加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.01,0:20:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別拿60分以下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.52,0:20:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙也很辛苦耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.02,0:20:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.60,0:20:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人現在還喊著要小暮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.81,0:21:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的沒有問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.81,0:21:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.02,0:21:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確保邊境方面的運輸路線的安全\N也是重要任務之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.97,0:21:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對護衛艦長的山本上尉以及對我們而言\N或許都是好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.12,0:21:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是說邊境路線出事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.58,0:21:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反而有助R計畫的推行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.87,0:21:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.85,0:21:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且可以把山本上尉與他們拉開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.17,0:21:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他們擅自行動，原本會成功的事情\N也會變得無法成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.01,0:21:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了要早一刻導入\NR計畫最重要的巡洋艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.01,0:21:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同時還得加快司令部內部的重新編組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.81,0:21:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必須早點讓泰勒艦長升官\N解除他的艦長職位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.65,0:21:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並發下讓微風號解體的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.11,0:21:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙不知會做何反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.11,0:21:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藤中將，你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.87,0:21:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.98,0:22:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好帥哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.58,0:22:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.87,0:22:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山本副艦長終於成為艦隊司令官了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.34,0:22:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以上太空了，太令人羨慕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.42,0:22:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，可以出擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.51,0:22:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想早點回太空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.51,0:22:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次的出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.47,0:22:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是去護送運輸船\N有點讓人缺乏鬥志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.39,0:22:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才沒有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.48,0:22:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.98,0:22:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我還要去整理資料課的剩餘工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.86,0:22:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八點開始艦長就任的慶祝會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.91,0:22:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經找海兵隊的人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.16,0:22:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.66,0:22:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想向拉爾康人還以顏色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.48,0:23:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是攻擊運輸船，這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.93,0:23:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉爾康他們有這麼小氣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.94,0:23:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抽出流星群的信號資料\N跟檢樣資料的成份分析後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.28,0:23:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有什麼差異?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.32,0:23:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.49,0:23:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只知道運輸船的消息中斷前後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.37,0:23:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有接受到帶磁流星裙特有的帶電訊號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.08,0:23:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及邊境空域附近\N沒有發現拉爾康戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.08,0:23:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後運輸船就被破壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.05,0:23:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運輸船被破壞跟無法鑑別的訊號\N有因果關係?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.80,0:23:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.39,0:23:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我提出的報告書上\N是說沒有因果關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.06,0:23:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也看過那個報告書了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.60,0:24:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電腦算出的結果是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.06,0:24:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法鑑別的信號其周波數成份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.61,0:24:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,及向量波形，都在帶電流星群的範圍內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.57,0:24:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然，這是單純的統計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.24,0:24:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎，可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.91,0:24:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有可能是拉爾康的新型武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.33,0:24:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，不是拉爾康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.54,0:24:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳有何依據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.29,0:24:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狙擊我的間諜說這個事故\N是拉爾康的新型武器造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.97,0:24:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果他說的是真的\N拉爾康就不必送間諜來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.60,0:24:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼他們為何派間諜來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.77,0:24:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說他的目的是惡化\N跟我們的敵對關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.48,0:24:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是拉爾康的話\N就很可能是意外事故了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.98,0:24:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題是邊境發生的事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.40,0:24:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何拉爾康人都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.32,0:24:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了，這其中一定另有蹊蹺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.73,0:25:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陛下，我主張要和平共處是因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:31.24,0:25:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自從先帝戈薩十五世治世之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.78,0:25:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本國士兵一直以打仗為傲\N置生死於度外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:39.16,0:25:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是經過漫長的休戰期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:42.33,0:25:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相對於敵人不穩動向日增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:44.63,0:25:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我軍的士兵卻士氣低落\N連戰鬥意志都喪失掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:54.80,0:25:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才你說的敵人的不穩動向是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:58.18,0:25:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再講清楚一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:59.97,0:26:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，第一\N行星聯合宇宙軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:04.48,0:26:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即將完成彈藥、防備都優秀的新型巡洋艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.15,0:26:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二，最近敵人派遣小規模的機動部隊\N及類似艦隊，在邊境空域徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:19.29,0:26:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅那瓦，是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:21.41,0:26:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:23.41,0:26:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旺克，繼續說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:24.79,0:26:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，敵人在休戰期間加強軍備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:28.17,0:26:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加強防衛線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.01,0:26:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然而我們拉爾康帝國空有\N不輸給敵人的軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:37.01,0:26:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們引以為傲的戰士\N卻全無戰鬥意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:43.10,0:26:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了顧慮帝國的將來\N與其等著吃敗仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:48.52,0:26:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如早點與敵人，行星聯合宇宙軍\N締結和平條約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:52.78,0:26:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才是聰明作法\N這是我身為宰相的建議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:58.62,0:27:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看怎樣，羅那瓦提督
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:01.33,0:27:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請恕我直言，陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.08,0:27:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們神聖拉爾康帝國的戰士\N軍心士氣不只沒有低落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:14.17,0:27:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反而是鬥志滿滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:17.39,0:27:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，兵士求戰的意願無從發洩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:19.93,0:27:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是無法隱瞞的事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:23.68,0:27:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是因為我們心高氣傲的戰士們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:26.23,0:27:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一心向著陛下呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:28.52,0:27:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅那瓦提督，你的意思是\N你反對和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:32.40,0:27:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陛下，請再用心考慮一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:34.82,0:27:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打戰講求所謂的勝機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:37.82,0:27:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時讓勝機溜過\N會無可避免招來敗仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:42.24,0:27:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅那瓦提督，我再問一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:45.08,0:27:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你反對和平嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:47.29,0:27:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自認我有能力率領全軍一鼓作氣殲滅敵人\N打敗行星聯合宇宙軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:56.42,0:28:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，那也只能逞一時之快\N真正為神聖拉爾康帝國的社稷考慮的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:00.89,0:28:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我贊成"真正"的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:04.31,0:28:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渾蛋，你知不知恥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:07.89,0:28:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為帝國軍的總帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:10.10,0:28:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有自信打贏，竟然想跟敵人和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:23.66,0:28:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肅靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:28.71,0:28:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅那瓦，你說現在打的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:31.33,0:28:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有自信打贏，真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:34.75,0:28:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，但是要求和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:38.13,0:28:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我們帝國軍人而言，並非恥辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:40.72,0:28:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平也是一種戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:42.72,0:28:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛說笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:44.47,0:28:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以打仗為榮的拉爾康帝國軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:47.81,0:28:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有自信打勝仗卻不肯打\N這算什麼勝利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:53.31,0:28:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果真如羅那瓦提督所言\N軍心士氣高昂，打仗必勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:59.32,0:29:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我旺克認為\N和平協定應當唾棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:03.20,0:29:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在應該對敵人\N行星聯合宇宙軍燃起戰火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:13.96,0:29:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外，應該調近衛師團\N去邊境對抗敵人的可能行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:21.43,0:29:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,且慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:24.30,0:29:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,近衛師團是保護陛下的直屬部隊呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:29.64,0:29:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟想派他們去殺敵\N真是太放肆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:32.77,0:29:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是直接道出那個需要罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:35.57,0:29:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒資格指使我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:38.11,0:29:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼你想怎麼處理\N敵人在邊境的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:42.11,0:29:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我自會考慮\N我倒希望你能花些心思考慮陛下的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:47.24,0:29:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，你太沒自信了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:50.62,0:29:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過移動一個師團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:53.21,0:29:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就無法保護陛下啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:58.05,0:30:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話不是那麼說，可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:00.55,0:30:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:02.22,0:30:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅那瓦，你說這場仗必勝是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:05.43,0:30:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，陛下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:07.14,0:30:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必派人保護朕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:09.31,0:30:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就實現你的諾言，打敗敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:12.06,0:30:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打一場不辱帝國威名的勝仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:14.73,0:30:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的給你們自己決定\N朕先退席了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:19.48,0:30:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:21.49,0:30:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陛下，請且慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:24.78,0:30:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭送陛下，陛下已經下令了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:44.05,0:30:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你該知道\N我們的邊境方面宇宙軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:46.43,0:30:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,位於防衛線的最偏遠地帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:50.52,0:30:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邊境空域廣大地區\N沒有足以成為軍事據點的星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:57.31,0:31:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是敵人不重視的未開發空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:03.82,0:31:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦這個防衛線被突破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:06.57,0:31:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人將可能侵入防衛線\N中央的背後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:10.20,0:31:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,切斷運輸路線\N給我軍毀滅性的打擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:16.71,0:31:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三船中將，避免這種事態的發生\N不是你的使命嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:23.17,0:31:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以從戰略考量來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:25.68,0:31:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強化邊境防衛軍是理所當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:29.47,0:31:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後，確保前線運輸路線的安全\N將變得越加重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:36.94,0:31:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外，設定迂迴運輸路線\N連結各方面軍力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:42.65,0:31:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在下相信那是我軍不可或缺的前提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:46.65,0:31:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請各位發表意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:49.91,0:31:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情報局長，請說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:53.62,0:31:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三船中將，前幾天情報局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:56.91,0:32:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接獲邊境方面單獨航行的運輸船\N遭受襲擊的報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:02.67,0:32:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,襲擊?這倒是第一次聽說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:05.26,0:32:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據我所知那是事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:07.88,0:32:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,調查部死與分析部\N都有分別調查這件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:11.72,0:32:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎樣，在目前的戰爭狀態下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:14.60,0:32:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無人能保證邊境就\N絕對不會出現敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:19.27,0:32:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:20.04,0:32:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過擊毀一艘運輸船\N還是無法改變戰局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:25.78,0:32:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:27.11,0:32:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於那件事，已經派護衛艦護航了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:31.62,0:32:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必我再解說邊境空域的\N運輸路線的重要性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:35.10,0:32:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信各位都已經理解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:38.62,0:32:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此一來，我們就需要機動性大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:41.17,0:32:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠在邊境迅速行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:44.42,0:32:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝備火力強大重武器的\N新型高速巡洋艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:51.26,0:32:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三船中將你講的新型高速巡洋艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:55.14,0:32:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是R號計畫中的配備呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:58.56,0:33:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為那件事\N已經轉到我的手頭上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:03.06,0:33:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是我誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:06.57,0:33:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幕僚議長，現在決定那件事還太早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:11.28,0:33:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們第四方面軍已經\N做好執行R號計畫的準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:16.87,0:33:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們第三方面軍也一樣\N置前線基地不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:20.83,0:33:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算什麼R號計畫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:34.30,0:33:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來和平的夢想轉眼即失，朕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:45.19,0:33:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陛下，陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:48.57,0:33:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生大事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:51.11,0:33:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比修拉姆受到攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:04.17,0:34:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才妳說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:23.69,0:34:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家已經意見一致了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:26.27,0:34:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的就只等陛下下令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:33.15,0:34:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:35.24,0:34:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的意思是除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:37.24,0:34:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以朕之名開戰之外\N沒別的法子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:40.79,0:34:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恕微臣斗膽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:42.04,0:34:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連比修拉姆領地都受到攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:45.12,0:34:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的已經別無辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:48.17,0:34:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先發制人是帝國開國以來的習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:54.43,0:35:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,貫徹這一點也是\N哥札十五世陛下的遺志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:07.98,0:35:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:10.98,0:35:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朕知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:18.66,0:35:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朕決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:20.87,0:35:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部的主力艦隊攻擊\N行星聯合宇宙軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:25.08,0:35:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打敗他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:37.84,0:35:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陛下，您的難過是必然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:40.47,0:35:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這是形勢所逼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:43.68,0:35:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夠了，朕已經決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:59.78,0:36:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到領國巡視過後\N已頓悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:03.95,0:36:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乍看之下平靜無事的我國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:07.42,0:36:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要跟行星聯合宇宙軍的\N交戰狀態持續下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:11.71,0:36:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會為國家體制招來失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:16.13,0:36:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:17.76,0:36:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何人都是那麼想\N連旺克也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:21.89,0:36:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼旺克宰相為何想要求和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:25.39,0:36:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他本來就不打算求和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:28.35,0:36:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他利用我的語病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:30.56,0:36:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奪得帝國軍的指揮決定權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:41.87,0:36:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特姆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:43.33,0:36:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要讓帝國存續下去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:45.66,0:36:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們軍人的想法\N必須做根本的改變才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:50.92,0:36:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是只有打敗敵人\N征服敵人才是戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:55.76,0:36:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:58.17,0:37:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看怎樣，三船中將
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:00.51,0:37:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邊境的運輸路線計畫\N就讓邊境方面軍來推行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:06.47,0:37:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如第一方面軍司令長官所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:09.60,0:37:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,R號計畫再重新檢討
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:13.65,0:37:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:16.07,0:37:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰得到新型高速巡洋艦\N誰就得到軍方的主導權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:21.66,0:37:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以每個部隊才拼命爭取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:29.00,0:37:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接受到拉爾哥傳來的\N非正式通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:31.96,0:37:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:32.83,0:37:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:34.34,0:37:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本帝國欲與行星聯合宇宙軍\N簽定和平協定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:41.51,0:37:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:49.89,0:37:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旺克大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:51.48,0:37:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:52.77,0:37:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾巴號發出不穩的訊號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:56.61,0:37:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道，別管它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:59.36,0:37:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:09.45,0:38:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅那瓦那傢伙竟然自以為聰明…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:15.63,0:38:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作夢也沒想到\N提督有那樣的意圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:20.59,0:38:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平也是戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:21.92,0:38:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平跟戰爭一樣是\N事關帝國的存亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:25.55,0:38:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這場戰爭\N無論如何一定要贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:29.22,0:38:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使我會被孤立起來也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:32.69,0:38:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次你得跟近衛師團一起去邊境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:37.15,0:38:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無法離開陛下\N所在的梅爾巴號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:41.11,0:38:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提督
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:42.65,0:38:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好，不管事態如何發展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:45.45,0:38:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你都不能忘記你是\N神聖拉爾哥帝國的軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:50.79,0:38:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧，時間快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:53.08,0:38:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:59.59,0:39:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅那瓦提督
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:00.96,0:39:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:02.51,0:39:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為比修拉姆不是受到\N行星聯合宇宙軍的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:08.43,0:39:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:09.68,0:39:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後請小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:21.53,0:39:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要求和?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:40.71,0:39:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?講和?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:44.09,0:39:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,近衛師團準備發動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:46.76,0:39:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟在巡洋艦特羅梅後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:51.68,0:39:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:25.97,0:40:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特羅梅號出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:56.00,0:41:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果保護陛下是\N帝國軍人的使命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:07.92,0:41:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平並非不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:28.28,0:41:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長，開始進入邊境空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:31.07,0:41:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，到下個座標點1628之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:34.12,0:41:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,切換為自動航行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:35.95,0:41:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解，到座標點1628之前\N切換為自動航行

